Description: Report-rendering layer for the Political Feasibility Module. A pure consumer of the
    curated Run-Group artifacts produced by the pfm compute layer: it reads them and renders the
    HTML reports and paper figures, performing no estimation or selection of its own. Ships the
    report templates and exposes one render function per report plus a renderGroup orchestrator.
